OBINNA EZUGWU Group Managing Director and Chief Executive Officer of Nigeria’s leading lender, Zenith Bank Plc., Mr. Ebenezer Onyeagwu, has congratulated Nigerians on the occasion of the country’s 60th Independence Anniversary. Onyeagwu in the congratulatory message on Thursday, however reminded all that the current generation must strive to make the country a land of peace, prosperity and opportunities for the future generation. “As we celebrate our 60th year of independence, let us remember we have a responsibility to make this nation a land of peace, prosperity and opportunities for those that we come after us,” Onyeagwu said. 